==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outwear
<hw>Out*wear"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
wear out; to consume or destroy by wearing.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To last longer than; to outlast; <as>as, this cloth
will <ex>outwear</ex> the other</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧If I the night
<xex>outwear</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outweary</ent>⟦br⟧
